
= Economist, University of Toulouse II, France. Scientific council of Attac-France

==Bio==
"Geneviève Azam is a lecturer in economics and a researcher at Toulouse University, France. She is also an environmental activist and "alter-globalist" for the organization Attac France."
(source: http://www.localfutures.org/growth-degrowth-brief-history/ )

